<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Certificate of Completion</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 50px;
      width: 842px; /* A4 landscape width in px at 96dpi */
      height: 595px; /* A4 landscape height in px at 96dpi */
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .border {
      border: 2px solid #0052cc;
      padding: 20px;
      height: 100%;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #0052cc;
      font-size: 30px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .name {
      color: #2684FF;
      font-size: 24px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 60px;
      width: 100%;
      left: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="border">
    <h1>Certificate of Completion</h1>
    <h2>Beks Coding Club Foundation Track</h2>
    <h3>Fundamentals of HTML and CSS</h3>
    <p>This certifies that</p>
    <div class="name"><%- firstName %> <%- lastName %>/div>
    <p>has successfully completed the course on</p>
    <p>Date: <%- completionDate %></p>
    <div class="footer">Issued by Beks Coding Club</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>